        <ontology:is_identified_by rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/appellation/Syrups"/>
        <ontology:partOfNarrative rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/narrative/N261_VC_15_CZ"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/49.5_16.0"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The MOVING reference member state of this VC (Value Chain) is CZECH REPUBLIC. The reference MOVING Card ID of this VC is VC 15 CZ. Syrup producers are not necessarily located in mountain areas. They collect ingredients from the mountain region and process the ingredients in nearby regions. Crucial part of the VC is the marketing that utilizes symbolic value of the region. There are examples of producers that organize their businesses as a social interprise with additional positive impacts in social areas.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


